---
import ComplianceNote from '../../../components/compliance/ComplianceNote.astro';
import CTAGroup from '../../../components/cta/CTAGroup.astro';
import CTASection from '../../../components/cta/CTASection.astro';
import ResponsiveImage from '../../../components/global/ResponsiveImage.astro';
import TopicCard from '../../../components/cards/TopicCard.astro';
import HeroSplit from '../../../components/sections/HeroSplit.astro';
import SectionIntro from '../../../components/sections/SectionIntro.astro';
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { contactLinks } from '../../../data/externalLinks';

const routineTopics = [
  {
    title: 'Calm & Stress',
    paragraphs: [
      'Many people keep going all day and only notice later how busy their mind has become.',
      'A small routine can help you pause for a moment and bring more calm into your day.',
      'This may involve scent, breathing, your surroundings, pauses or small rituals.',
      'Essential oils can be included when they are used appropriately and responsibly.',
    ],
    cta: 'Discuss a Calming Routine',
  },
  {
    title: 'Sleep & Evening Routine',
    paragraphs: [
      'A good evening often begins before you go to bed.',
      'Many people would like a more considered transition from day to night.',
      'An evening routine can help bring the day to a clearer close and create a calmer atmosphere.',
      'This might involve a room fragrance, an established ritual, a short pause or a simple application.',
      'What matters is that the routine fits your life and does not feel like another task.',
    ],
    cta: 'Explore an Evening Routine',
  },
  {
    title: 'Energy & Focus',
    paragraphs: [
      'Sometimes the day needs greater clarity.',
      'Many people look for a simple way to approach their day more consciously, whether in the morning, at work or in between.',
      'Routines involving scent, structure, movement, freshness or high-quality wellness products may be of interest here.',
      'The aim is not to push yourself artificially.',
      'It is about creating intentional moments that can support you in daily life.',
    ],
    cta: 'Discuss a Daytime Routine',
  },
  {
    title: 'Family & Everyday Life',
    paragraphs: [
      'In family life especially, a routine should be simple, safe and realistic.',
      'Parents often want to explore natural options while being understandably cautious.',
      'That is a good thing.',
      'Clear, responsible advice is particularly important for families and children.',
      'Not every oil, application or recommendation is automatically right for every situation.',
      'I help you look calmly and clearly at what may be right for you and what to keep in mind.',
    ],
    cta: 'Discuss a Family Routine',
  },
  {
    title: 'Home & Everyday Alternatives',
    paragraphs: [
      'Many people want to take a more considered approach to their home and use fewer conventional household products.',
      'Essential oils and natural products can have a useful role here.',
      'For example, for room fragrance, freshness, cleaning or small household routines.',
      'The same applies here:',
      'Not everything needs to change immediately.',
      'A simple first step that feels right and is easy to implement is often enough.',
    ],
    cta: 'Discuss a Natural Home Routine',
  },
  {
    title: 'Daily Wellness & Nutritional Supplements',
    paragraphs: [
      'Alongside essential oils, doTERRA also offers high-quality wellness products and nutritional supplements.',
      'This may be of interest to people who want to take a more considered approach over the long term and complement their daily routines.',
      'This can include topics such as general wellbeing, conscious nutrition, daily life, energy, balance or systems such as MetaPWR.',
      'Honest advice is important here too.',
      'Not every product suits every person. That is why we look together at what fits your goals, daily life and current needs.',
    ],
    cta: 'Discuss a Wellness Routine',
  },
];
---

<PageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Essential Oils and Daily Routines"
  description="Essential oils do not have to be complicated."
>
  <HeroSplit
    title="Essential Oils as Part of Your Daily Routine"
    primaryHref="/en/contact/"
    primaryLabel="Discuss a Suitable Routine"
    secondaryHref={contactLinks.whatsapp.href}
    secondaryLabel="Message Me on WhatsApp"
    imageSrc="/assets/images/products/essential-oils-display.jpg"
    imageAlt="Essential oils arranged clearly in a wooden holder"
    imageWidth={2400}
    imageHeight={3600}
    imagePosition="54% center"
  >
    <p>Essential oils do not have to be complicated.</p>
    <p>For many people, getting started does not begin with a particular product, but with a simple question:</p>
    <p>What would I like in my daily life?</p>
    <p>More calm.<br />A more considered evening.<br />More energy in the morning.<br />A more pleasant home.<br />Natural household alternatives.<br />More structure for small wellness routines.</p>
    <p>This is where essential oils and natural routines may become relevant.</p>
    <p>Not as a quick solution for everything.<br />Not as a substitute for medical treatment.<br />But as considered additions to your daily routine.</p>
    <p>I help you understand these options and find out what genuinely suits you.</p>
  </HeroSplit>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container narrow-layout">
      <SectionIntro title="Everyday Life First, Then the Product">
        <p>Many people begin with the question:</p>
        <p>“Which oil do I need?”</p>
        <p>In my view, the better question is:</p>
        <p>“What would I like to make easier, calmer or more considered in my daily life?”</p>
        <p>A product recommendation is only useful once the real aim is clear.</p>
        <p>Perhaps you do not need a large selection.<br />Perhaps a simple start is enough.<br />Perhaps a starter kit is the right choice.<br />Perhaps the first step is simply understanding use and options.</p>
        <p>My support helps you make a considered start instead of buying products blindly.</p>
      </SectionIntro>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split-layout">
      <div>
        <SectionIntro title="Keeping Natural Routines Simple">
          <p>A natural routine is not a complicated programme.</p>
          <p>It can be a small moment that you regularly build into daily life.</p>
          <p>A scent in the morning.<br />A calm close to the evening.<br />A conscious pause in between.<br />A pleasant room fragrance.<br />A natural household alternative.<br />A regular moment for you or your family.</p>
          <p>The goal is not perfection.</p>
          <p>The goal is to find simple things that you will genuinely use and that fit naturally into your life.</p>
        </SectionIntro>
      </div>
      <ResponsiveImage
        src="/assets/images/products/diffuser-lemon.jpg"
        alt="Diffuser and lemon essential oil in a calm setting"
        width={3600}
        height={2400}
        variant="portrait-wide"
        position="58% center"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--sage">
    <div class="container">
      <SectionIntro title="Areas We Can Explore Together" />
      <div class="topic-grid">
        {routineTopics.map((topic) => (
          <TopicCard title={topic.title}>
            {topic.paragraphs.map((paragraph) => <p>{paragraph}</p>)}
            <CTAGroup primaryHref="/en/contact/" primaryLabel={topic.cta} />
          </TopicCard>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--nature">
    <div class="container narrow-layout">
      <SectionIntro title="Why Personal Guidance Is Helpful">
        <p>doTERRA offers a broad range of products.</p>
        <p>That is exciting, but it can also feel overwhelming at first.</p>
        <p>Single oils.<br />Oil blends.<br />Starter kits.<br />Personal care products.<br />Household products.<br />Nutritional supplements.<br />Wellness systems.</p>
        <p>When you browse the shop alone, it is not always easy to tell which products are right for you.</p>
        <p>That is why the best first step is often a short conversation rather than a purchase.</p>
        <p>We clarify what you are looking for, what you already know and which starting point may be right for you.</p>
      </SectionIntro>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container split-layout split-layout--reverse">
      <ResponsiveImage
        src="/assets/images/products/product-detail-01.png"
        alt="Essential oils on a wooden plate in warm daylight"
        width={1672}
        height={941}
        variant="portrait-wide"
        position="62% center"
      />
      <div>
        <SectionIntro title="A Simple Way to Begin">
          <p>You briefly tell me what interests you.</p>
          <p>I ask a few simple questions so that I can better understand your needs.</p>
          <p>Then we consider the available options.</p>
          <p>This could be a small routine.<br />A single product.<br />A starter kit.<br />A doTERRA customer account.<br />Or simply a clear answer to your questions for now.</p>
          <p>When you begin through me, an official doTERRA customer account allows you to purchase products at wholesale pricing and save 25% on your purchases. At the same time, you have someone you can contact for personal support.</p>
        </SectionIntro>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow-layout">
      <SectionIntro title="What Matters to Me">
        <p>I want you to understand what you are using.</p>
        <p>I want you to feel confident.</p>
        <p>I do not want you to buy more than you need at the beginning.</p>
        <p>And I want you to know how to use your products in daily life even after your purchase.</p>
        <p>Good routines do not come from pressure.</p>
        <p>They grow from clarity, simplicity and the right support.</p>
      </SectionIntro>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="The Simplest Next Step"
    primaryHref="/en/contact/"
    primaryLabel="Discuss a Suitable Routine"
    secondaryHref={contactLinks.whatsapp.href}
    secondaryLabel="Message Me on WhatsApp"
  >
    <p>You do not need to know which oil you need.</p>
    <p>You do not need to know which kit is right.</p>
    <p>You do not need to be sure yet whether doTERRA is right for you.</p>
    <p>Simply tell me which topic interests you.</p>
    <p>Then we can find out which next step is right.</p>
  </CTASection>

  <section class="compliance-section">
    <div class="container">
      <ComplianceNote label="Note">
        <h2>A Brief Note</h2>
        <p>My support is not a substitute for medical diagnosis or treatment.<br />I do not claim that products can diagnose, treat or cure medical conditions.</p>
        <p>Essential oils, wellness products and natural routines can be part of a considered daily routine, but they do not replace medical or therapeutic care.</p>
        <p>If you have health concerns or medical questions, please consult a doctor or another appropriately qualified healthcare professional.</p>
      </ComplianceNote>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .section { padding: var(--space-64) 0; }
  .section--cream { background: var(--color-soft-cream); }
  .section--sage { background: rgb(168 184 160 / 20%); }
  .section--nature { position: relative; isolation: isolate; background: var(--color-soft-cream); }
  .section--nature::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: -2; background: url('/assets/images/nature/nature-heath-hero-02.png') center 52% / cover no-repeat; }
  .section--nature::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: -1; background: rgb(250 247 241 / 76%); }
  .narrow-layout { max-width: var(--container-text); }
  .split-layout { display: grid; gap: var(--space-40); align-items: center; }
  .topic-grid { display: grid; gap: var(--space-20); }
  .topic-grid :global(.topic-card > div) { display: flex; height: calc(100% - 52px); flex-direction: column; }
  .topic-grid :global(.topic-card p) { margin: 0 0 var(--space-12); }
  .topic-grid :global(.topic-card p:last-of-type) { margin-bottom: var(--space-24); }
  .topic-grid :global(.topic-card .cta-group) { margin-top: auto; }
  .compliance-section { padding: 0 0 var(--space-80); }
  .compliance-section :global(h2) { margin: 0 0 var(--space-12); font-size: var(--font-size-body-mobile); }
  .compliance-section :global(p + p) { margin-top: var(--space-12); }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section { padding-block: var(--space-96); }
    .topic-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-24); }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section { padding-block: var(--space-120); }
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(360px, .8fr); gap: var(--space-80); }
    .split-layout--reverse { grid-template-columns: minmax(360px, .8fr) minmax(0, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
